name: Willy Woni-corn: Nouns at ETH Denver 2024!
description:
Introducing Willy Woni-corn, our mascot for Nouns at ETH Denver 2024. Collect this Limited edition one-of-a-kind piece by Frankie Colamarino to celebrate Nouns taking Denver by storm!

Join us for an unforgettable series of events and activations all week long: 

NOUNS FUNDS CODE:
Day One of BUIDLer Nights at the BUIDLHub. Enjoy free food and refreshments while you learn about how you can bring your infrastructure and engineering skills to bear within Nouns, and participate in a 1 ETH BUIDLer LIVE Prop House Hackathon! 

NOUNS FUNDS COMMUNITY: 
Day 2 of BUIDLer Nights, this session is dedicated to mentoring builders on Prophouse ideation and crafting compelling proposals, with insights into the many diverse communities supported by Nouns DAO.

NOUNS FUNDS CREATORS:
An intimate offsite social gathering featuring live painting and musical guests punctuated by chill vibes, free food and drinks. 

EXCLUSIVE MERCH:

Check out our crypto-enabled Nouns Vending Machine on the main floor of the convention, where you can unlock incredible custom-designed Nouns X ETH Denver  Merchandise!

THE GOLDEN TICKET RAFFLE

We'll also be selling bespoke Golden Ticket Nouns Chocolate bars all week long for $3, with proceeds going to the Tornado Devs Legal Fund. One lucky person will discover a secret Golden Ticket and win a prize package worth more than 1 ETH!
